{"openapi":"3.0.1","info":{"title":"ESP32 Telemetry Collection Service","description":"A self-hosted Kotlin Spring Boot service that collects telemetry data from ESP32 devices via HTTP API calls and forwards the data to Grafana's collector. \nThe service provides data validation, authentication, and comprehensive observability features.\n\n## Features\n- API key-based authentication for ESP32 clients\n- Data validation with whitelist-based filtering for Prometheus metrics\n- Size limit enforcement for OTEL data and events arrays\n- Comprehensive error handling and logging\n- Health check endpoints and metrics exposure\n- Structured JSON logging with MDC context\n\n## Authentication\nThe service uses API key authentication. Include a valid API key in the `X-API-Key` header for all requests.","contact":{"name":"ESP32 Telemetry Service Team","email":"support@telemetry-service.com"},"license":{"name":"MIT","url":"https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT"},"version":"1.0.0"},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:8080","description":"Local development server"},{"url":"https://telemetry-service.example.com","description":"Production server"}],"security":[{"ApiKeyAuth":[]}],"tags":[{"name":"Telemetry","description":"Telemetry data collection endpoints"},{"name":"Metrics","description":"Metrics and monitoring endpoints"},{"name":"Actuator","description":"Monitor and interact","externalDocs":{"description":"Spring Boot Actuator Web API Documentation","url":"https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/current/actuator-api/html/"}},{"name":"Health","description":"Health check endpoints for monitoring"}],"paths":{"/api/v1/telemetry":{"post":{"tags":["Telemetry"],"summary":"Submit telemetry data from ESP32 device","description":"Submit a batch of telemetry data including OpenTelemetry metrics, events, and Prometheus metrics. The service validates the data and forwards it to Grafana collector. Validation Rules: Prometheus metrics are filtered using a whitelist, OTEL data size is limited, Events array size is limited. Rate Limits: Maximum 1000 OTEL metrics, 100 events, 100 Prometheus metrics per request.","operationId":"receiveTelemetryData","requestBody":{"description":"Telemetry data batch from ESP32 device","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TelemetryBatchRequest"},"examples":{"validRequest":{"summary":"Valid telemetry request with all data types","description":"validRequest","value":{"deviceId":"esp32-001","timestamp":"2025-07-20T10:30:00Z","otel":[{"name":"system.cpu.usage","value":45.2,"labels":{"core":"0"},"timestamp":"2025-07-20T10:30:00Z"}],"events":[{"type":"wifi.connected","message":"Connected to WiFi network","severity":"INFO","timestamp":"2025-07-20T10:29:58Z","metadata":{"ssid":"IoT-Network","rssi":-45}}],"metrics":[{"name":"esp32_temperature_celsius","value":23.5,"labels":{"sensor":"internal"},"help":"ESP32 internal temperature","type":"gauge"}]}},"minimalRequest":{"summary":"Minimal valid request","description":"minimalRequest","value":{"deviceId":"esp32-002","timestamp":"2025-07-20T10:30:00Z"}}}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Telemetry data processed successfully","content":{"application/json":{"examples":{"success":{"summary":"Successfully processed without warnings","description":"success","value":{"status":"accepted","validatedMetrics":5,"truncatedOtel":false,"truncatedEvents":false,"droppedPrometheusMetrics":0}},"successWithWarnings":{"summary":"Successfully processed with warnings","description":"successWithWarnings","value":{"status":"accepted_with_warnings","validatedMetrics":3,"truncatedOtel":true,"truncatedEvents":false,"droppedPrometheusMetrics":2,"warnings":["OTEL data truncated due to size limit","Dropped 2 non-whitelisted Prometheus metrics"]}}}}}},"400":{"description":"Bad request - invalid JSON or validation failed","content":{"application/json":{"examples":{"invalidJson":{"summary":"Invalid JSON format","description":"invalidJson","value":{"error":"Bad Request","message":"Invalid JSON format","path":"/api/v1/telemetry"}},"validationFailed":{"summary":"Request validation failed","description":"validationFailed","value":{"error":"Validation Failed","message":"Request validation failed","path":"/api/v1/telemetry","details":["deviceId: Device ID cannot be blank","timestamp: Timestamp cannot be null"]}}}}}},"401":{"description":"Unauthorized - invalid or missing API key","content":{"application/json":{}}},"500":{"description":"Internal server error","content":{"application/json":{}}}},"security":[{"ApiKeyAuth":[]}]}},"/actuator":{"get":{"tags":["Actuator"],"summary":"Actuator root web endpoint","operationId":"links","responses":{"200":{"description":"OK","content":{"application/vnd.spring-boot.actuator.v3+json":{"schema":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Link"}}}},"application/vnd.spring-boot.actuator.v2+json":{"schema":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Link"}}}},"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Link"}}}}}}}}},"/actuator/prometheus":{"get":{"tags":["Metrics","Actuator"],"summary":"Prometheus metrics endpoint","description":"Exposes Prometheus metrics for monitoring the telemetry service. Includes request metrics, validation metrics, forwarding metrics, and system metrics.","operationId":"prometheus","responses":{"200":{"description":"Prometheus metrics in text format","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"type":"string"}},"text/plain;version=0.0.4;charset=utf-8":{"schema":{"type":"object"}},"application/openmetrics-text;version=1.0.0;charset=utf-8":{"schema":{"type":"object"}}}}}}},"/actuator/health":{"get":{"tags":["Health","Actuator"],"summary":"Get overall health status","description":"Returns the overall health status of the application","operationId":"health","responses":{"200":{"description":"Health status","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Health"}},"application/vnd.spring-boot.actuator.v3+json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}},"application/vnd.spring-boot.actuator.v2+json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}},"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}}}}}}},"/actuator/health/readiness":{"get":{"tags":["Health"],"summary":"Readiness health check","description":"Readiness probe indicates if the application is ready to serve traffic. Used by Kubernetes to determine if the container is ready to accept requests.","operationId":"getReadiness","responses":{"200":{"description":"Application is ready","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Health"}}}},"503":{"description":"Application is not ready","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Health"}}}}}}},"/actuator/health/liveness":{"get":{"tags":["Health"],"summary":"Liveness health check","description":"Liveness probe indicates if the application is running. Used by Kubernetes to restart the container if it's no longer alive.","operationId":"getLiveness","responses":{"200":{"description":"Application is alive","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Health"}}}},"503":{"description":"Application is not alive","content":{"*/*":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Health"}}}}}}},"/actuator/health/**":{"get":{"tags":["Actuator"],"summary":"Actuator web endpoint 'health-path'","operationId":"health-path","responses":{"200":{"description":"OK","content":{"application/vnd.spring-boot.actuator.v3+json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}},"application/vnd.spring-boot.actuator.v2+json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}},"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"Event":{"required":["message","severity","timestamp","type"],"type":"object","properties":{"type":{"maxLength":50,"minLength":1,"pattern":"^[a-zA-Z0-9_.-]+$","type":"string"},"message":{"maxLength":1000,"minLength":1,"type":"string"},"severity":{"pattern":"^(DEBUG|INFO|WARN|ERROR|FATAL)$","type":"string"},"timestamp":{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},"metadata":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"type":"object"}}}},"OtelMetric":{"required":["labels","name","timestamp","value"],"type":"object","properties":{"name":{"maxLength":100,"minLength":1,"type":"string"},"value":{"maximum":,"exclusiveMaximum":false,"minimum":-,"exclusiveMinimum":false,"type":"number","format":"double"},"labels":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"maxLength":50,"minLength":0,"type":"string"}},"timestamp":{"type":"string","format":"date-time"}}},"PrometheusMetric":{"required":["labels","name","value"],"type":"object","properties":{"name":{"maxLength":100,"minLength":1,"pattern":"^[a-zA-Z_:][a-zA-Z0-9_:]*$","type":"string"},"value":{"maximum":,"exclusiveMaximum":false,"minimum":-,"exclusiveMinimum":false,"type":"number","format":"double"},"labels":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"maxLength":30,"minLength":0,"type":"string"}},"help":{"maxLength":500,"minLength":0,"type":"string"},"type":{"pattern":"^(counter|gauge|histogram|summary)$","type":"string"}}},"TelemetryBatchRequest":{"required":["deviceId","timestamp"],"type":"object","properties":{"deviceId":{"maxLength":50,"minLength":1,"type":"string"},"timestamp":{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},"otel":{"maxItems":1000,"minItems":0,"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/OtelMetric"}},"events":{"maxItems":100,"minItems":0,"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Event"}},"metrics":{"maxItems":100,"minItems":0,"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/PrometheusMetric"}}}},"Link":{"type":"object","properties":{"href":{"type":"string"},"templated":{"type":"boolean"}}},"Health":{"type":"object","properties":{"description":{"type":"string"},"status":{"type":"string"},"details":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"type":"object"}}}}},"securitySchemes":{"ApiKeyAuth":{"type":"apiKey","description":"API key for authenticating ESP32 devices.\n\nConfigure valid API keys using the `TELEMETRY_API_KEYS` environment variable:\n```\nTELEMETRY_API_KEYS=esp32-device-key-001,esp32-device-key-002,esp32-device-key-003\n```","name":"X-API-Key","in":"header"}}}}